\newlabel{fig:double_slit}{{3}{9}{Double-slit experiment in two coherence frames. Left: interference frame~$\Fint $ shows the characteristic fringe pattern. Right: which-path frame~$\Fwp $ resolves individual paths with no interference. The Born measure $\mu (L) = \mu (R) = 1/2$ is invariant}{figure.3}{}}
